18 (17) "Practice of respiratory care" means the procedures employed in the therapy,
19 management, rehabilitation, gathering of assessment information, or other
20 procedures administered to patients with deficiencies or abnormalities that affect
21 their cardiopulmonary system and associated aspects of cardiopulmonary and
22 other system functions. This includes but is not limited to the:
23 (a) Provision of respiratory care procedures to ensure the safety, comfort,
