19 (5) years from the date of the expiration shall not be required to submit to
20 any examination as a condition to reinstatement. A reinstatement applicant
21 shall show compliance with the current continuing education requirement
22 in force at the time of the license reinstatement application.
23 (d) A person shall not practice respiratory care in this state unless the
24 individual holds an active license.
